{"tid":2222202,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"為咗唔好畀hater/劣幣激親我, 但又要照顧認真學炒股票嘅人, 唯有咁.....","createTime":"2020-09-29T02:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T09:56:12.000Z","uid":353278,"like":26,"dislike":85,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"5e3a5aedecdb4e4c6b0261278aafe674c4cc43ce","tid":2222202,"uid":353278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:45:57.000Z","msg":"劣幣驅逐良幣<br />\n唔會再講我嘅實時買賣, 唔會講我嘅倉<br />\n但就會介紹有趣股票<br />\n<br />\n有大志嘅人炒股票梗係想發達, 想發達就要發掘 next big thing. 發掘嘅過程大部分失敗 (咁容易冇人返工), 關鍵就係發掘失敗都唔好輸大錢. 發掘到一隻成功, 財務自由之路已經可以成功一半.<br />\n<br />\nLiquid biospy : early detection of cancer<br />\n三間公司賽跑緊<br />\n<br />\nEXAS: 股價走勢反映市場最睇好, 最近嗰個 investor conference 搞到分析員好興奮, 我睇過presentation就覺得唔係太特別<br />\n<br />\nILMN: 絕對龍頭, 基因分析儀器壟斷地位, 擁有最多data, 不過衰在上一屆ceo屎忽痕, 賣咗大部分 grail 股權, 現任ceo糾正錯誤, 唯有高價買返, 但係市場就唔係咁鍾意佢低賣高買, 所以股價受挫<br />\n<br />\nGH: 都係好嘢, 市場覺得佢都有機會, 尤其是佢係第一隻 &quot;First FDA-Approved Liquid Biopsy for Comprehensive Tumor Mutation Profiling Across All Solid Cancers&quot;<br />\n<br />\n我覺得Liquid biospy multiple cancer early detection搞得掂係遲早問題, 好多人都想有依樣測試年年驗身 (including me), 保險公司其實都想, 因為醫中後期癌症成本好高.....<br />\n<br />\n認真學炒股票嘅人可以自己發掘多啲資料, 再share出嚟畀大家分享<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25db4d94bddb9e36b1dc5e40a57106f0f1f4d765","tid":2222202,"uid":80866,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:46:43.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"387282525405dc6d1c8e3132e06785e30c0d9968","tid":2222202,"uid":194690,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6508afc8b06cf1bcc32b01fd55b0fb98dced0c9","tid":2222202,"uid":186666,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:48:59.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" 