m/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.globenewswire.com%2Fnews-release%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F1003870%2F0%2Fzh-hant%2FGRAIL%25E8%2588%2587Cirina%25E5%2590%2588%25E4%25BD%25B5-%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E5%2589%25B5%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E6%2596%25BC%25E7%2599%258C%25E7%2597%2587%25E6%2597%25A9%25E6%259C%259F%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%2592%25B0%25E7%2590%2583%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8.html&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXAmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=cca12b4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2017/05/31/1003870/0/zh-hant/GRAIL%E8%88%87Cirina%E5%90%88%E4%BD%B5-%E4%BB%A5%E5%89%B5%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%B6%E5%B0%88%E6%B3%A8%E6%96%BC%E7%99%8C%E7%97%87%E6%97%A9%E6%9C%9F%E6%B8%AC%E8%A9%A6%E7%9A%84%E7%92%B0%E7%90%83%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8.html</a>"},{"pid":"47a1921c93793fe502494db7f27cb79b851d5b32","tid":2222202,"uid":38448,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:03:23.000Z","msg":"嚟緊呢幾年我都好睇genome/biotech sector<br />\n但唔太有信心揀個股 所以直接買契媽既ARKG <br />\n<br />\n啱啱check check 見ARKG都有買你講呢三隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然持倉比例唔算高<br />\n<br />\n希望一兩年內ARKG追上ARKK既價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5789ac3de11e938f8dc1d6e7272edc6f99e4d905","tid":2222202,"uid":353278,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T03:13:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YmcSmy3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYmcSmy3.jpg&h=58f79128&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDennis Lo, MD, PhD, is the Director of the Li Ka Shing Institute of Health Sciences, the Li Ka Shing Professor of Medicine, and Professor of Chemical Pathology at The Chinese University of Hong Kong (CUHK). Dr. Lo was the first scientist to discover the presence of circulating fetal DNA in a pregnant mother&rsquo;s blood plasma and is a key driver of noninvasive prenatal testing (NIPT). He sees parallels between the release of DNA from a fetus into the bloodstream of its mother and the release of DNA from a tumor into the bloodstream of a cancer patient. Over the last 20 years, he has made many original discoveries on the biological characteristics of circulating fetal and tumor DNA, and has developed many innovative technologies for plasma nucleic acids-based molecular diagnostics. Dr. Lo has been recognized with numerous prestigious awards and honors for his contributions, including the 2016 Future Science Prize in Life Sciences. He was elected as a Fellow of the Royal Society (FRS) in 2011 and as a Foreign Associate of the US National Academy of Sciences in 2013. Dr. Lo holds a BA from the University of Cambridge, and holds an MD and a PhD from the University of Oxford."},{"pid":"cb83fc7bba93c280cc8187f958c83c4619de4e27","tid":2222202,"uid":9784,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5e3a5aedecdb4e4c6b0261278aafe674c4cc43ce","tid":2222202,"uid":353278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T02:45:57.000Z","msg":"劣幣驅逐良幣<br />\n唔會再講我嘅實時買賣, 唔會講我嘅倉<br />\n但就會介紹有趣股票<br />\n<br />\n有大志嘅人炒股票梗係想發達, 想發達就要發掘 next big thing. 發掘嘅過程大部分失敗 (咁容易冇人返工), 關鍵就係發掘失敗都唔好輸大錢. 發掘到一隻成功, 財務自由之路已經可以成功一半.<br />\n<br />\nLiquid biospy : early detection of cancer<br />\n三間公司賽跑緊<br />\n<br />\nEXAS: 股價走勢反映市場最睇好, 最近嗰個 investor conference 搞到分析員好興奮, 我睇過presentation就覺得唔係太特別<br />\n<br />\nILMN: 絕對龍頭, 基因分析儀器壟斷地位, 擁有最多data, 不過衰在上一屆ceo屎忽痕, 賣咗大部分 grail 股權, 現任ceo糾正錯誤, 唯有高價買返, 但係市場就唔係咁鍾意佢低賣高買, 所以股價受挫<br />\n<br />\nGH: 都係好嘢, 市場覺得佢都有機會, 尤其是佢係第一隻 &quot;First FDA-Approved Liquid Biopsy for Comprehensive Tumor Mutation Profiling Across All Solid Cancers&quot;<br />\n<br />\n我覺得Liquid biospy multiple cancer early detection搞得掂係遲早問題, 好多人都想有依樣測試年年驗身 (including me), 保險公司其實都想, 因為醫中後期癌症成本好高.....<br />\n<br />\n認真學炒股票嘅人可以自己發掘多啲資料, 再share出嚟畀大家分享<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" 